data.title: Actor James Brolin on "Sweet Tooth" and nearly 25-year marriage to Barbra Streisand
data.meta_description: Actor James Brolin joins "CBS Mornings" to discuss Season 2 of the Netflix series "Sweet Tooth." The series is based on the DC comic book series by Jeff Lemire. Brolin discusses narrating the show and his nearly 25-year marriage to Barbra Streisand.
